    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343580/extras/2a0cadd38996cf2622371d058c801c6a.avif?t=1772225743\" width=840 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343580/extras/0e08df00be5592a42abce597df3f46ce.poster.avif?t=1772225743\" width=800 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343580/extras/0e08df00be5592a42abce597df3f46ce.webm?t=1772225743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343580/extras/0e08df00be5592a42abce597df3f46ce.mp4?t=1772225743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><u>The Ghouls are coming for you!</u></strong><strong>  Play like your life is at stake and defend yourself from these terrifying and scary creatures, from farty strong zombies, to deadly mafia skeletons that will put you down, survive 3 waves to beat the game!! With increasing difficulty and Cursed waves with new challenges  </strong>   <br><strong>  </strong>  <br><strong> ¿Can you survive this insanity?</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>PUNCH THE GHOULS BRUTALLY!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343580/extras/e0ccd204b53fda27452e3836ef6298b3.poster.avif?t=1772225743\" width=800 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343580/extras/e0ccd204b53fda27452e3836ef6298b3.webm?t=1772225743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343580/extras/e0ccd204b53fda27452e3836ef6298b3.mp4?t=1772225743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>DAMN! That's a lotta damage!!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Use your bare-knuckle</strong> <strong>combat to deal with the Ghouls in many cool ways, from simple punching, heavy charges and lethal grabs, DON'T LET THEM HURT YOU!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>DEADLY ABSURD MAYHEM</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343580/extras/f51fdc5002808bd0ed067e4c32732166.poster.avif?t=1772225743\" width=800 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343580/extras/f51fdc5002808bd0ed067e4c32732166.webm?t=1772225743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343580/extras/f51fdc5002808bd0ed067e4c32732166.mp4?t=1772225743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>THIS IS GOING NUTS!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Use your environment as a weapon, grab props to attack the Ghouls, throw them with a heavy attack launch and stomp their heads into the ground, this is a literal playground of violence, use it!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
